name: MELIORA - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character KITTO, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21.MELIORA loves to collect NFTs and they have so many of them. So many of them that they have now used them to make a large nest on the tallest rainbow mountain in URCORNYVERSE and it still gets bigger and bigger. MELIORA can afford so many NFTs as she lays crypto coins whenever she needs them.
